list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add project configuration files and .gitignore
New project configuration files have been added for IntelliJ including modules.xml, workspace.xml, misc.xml, Pong.iml, and vcs.xml. Additionally, a .gitignore file has been created to ignore unnecessary and system-dependent files, which includes rules for IntelliJ, Eclipse, NetBeans, VS Code and MacOS related files.
